<li><a href="/blogs/recipe/tagged/スイーツ"><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0262/8252/4717/files/recipe-cate03.jpg"><h4>スイーツ</h4></a></li>
<li><a href="/blogs/recipe/tagged/ご飯-パン-麺"><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0262/8252/4717/files/recipe-cate004.jpg"><h4>ご飯・パン・麺</h4></a></li>
